Subject: Re: [T2] Adjusting Vanagon valves

Mike Soultanian wrote:
  can I adjust hydraulic valves with the
  engine still warm?
Yes, and being fully pumped up, the lifters will be tighter.  However, 
you can burn your fingers if too hot..........
Loosen setting nut way back and hand crank it in to feel when it just 
makes contact before screwing in 3 180 deg rotations of screwdriver.
